parameters.name: FileName
parameters.description: Sprites API: The name of the sprite ï¬le to retrieve, following pattern sprites(@2x)?\.(png|json). Example: sprites.png.

parameters.name: Style
parameters.description: Style specifies the desired map style for the Sprites APIs.

parameters.name: ColorScheme
parameters.description: Sets color tone for map such as dark and light for specific map styles. It applies to only vector map styles such as Standard and Monochrome. Example: Light Default value: Light.

parameters.name: Variant
parameters.description: Optimizes map styles for specific use case or industry. You can choose allowed variant only with Standard map style. Example: Default.

nested_items.name: Blob
nested_items.description: The body of the sprite sheet or JSON offset file (image/png or application/json, depending on input).

nested_items.name: ContentType
nested_items.description: Header that represents the format of the response. The response returns the following as the HTTP body.

nested_items.name: CacheControl
nested_items.description: Header that instructs caching configuration for the client.
